&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Freelance Medical Writer &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Healthcare Consultancy Group (HCG) is seeking a freelance medical writer with strong medical writing experience in a Medical Communications agency working on projects in Publications. Medical Affairs and/or Promotional Medical Communications (Med Ed).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Required Skills/Experience&lt;/p&gt;
